Details: Mail-order pharmacies are a great choice for “maintenance drugs,” or prescriptions you take regularly, such as birth control pills or blood pressure meds.
Where in article: Between first and second graf
When surveyed, 91% of pharmacists said they buy generic, store-brand headache remedies instead of brand-name ones.

Details: According to a 2019 Consumer Reports survey, 30% of Americans who currently take a prescription drug regularly say their out-of-pocket cost for that drug had gone up in the previous year. Of those, 12% said their costs went up by $100 or more.
